{"content": "I need to multiply 425\u2089 \u00d7 347\u2089.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n425\u2089 = 4\u00d79\u00b2 + 2\u00d79\u00b9 + 5\u00d79\u2070 = 4\u00d781 + 2\u00d79 + 5\u00d71 = 324 + 18 + 5 = 347\u2081\u2080\n\n347\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 4\u00d79\u00b9 + 7\u00d79\u2070 = 3\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 7\u00d71 = 243 + 36 + 7 = 286\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n347 \u00d7 286 = 99,242\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n99242 \u00f7 9 = 11027 r 5\n11027 \u00f7 9 = 1225 r 2\n1225 \u00f7 9 = 136 r 1\n136 \u00f7 9 = 15 r 1\n15 \u00f7 9 = 1 r 6\n1 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 1\n\nReading from bottom to top: **161125\u2089**\n\n161125", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 325}